28 Jul 2006
* Octopus now handles instancing of meshes (affects .mesh and .scene export)
  - Only one mesh is exported for a set of instances.
  - The mesh is determined by the first instance (of a set of instances) encountered
    in the scene or selection set.

09 Mar 2005
* adjusted to latest dotScene format
* new persistent settings (octopusScript.ini): units scale, temporary XML file policy and flip Y/Z
* adjusted to latest dotLink format ("complex" is now "actor")
* fixed various issues with Y/Z flipping and relative coordinates for dotScene
* fixed various issues with Y/Z flipping and relative coordinates for dotXODE

